### Add a new food
POST http://localhost:5000/api/v1/admin/foods
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

{
    "name": "Pizza Margherita",
    "cuisine": "Italian",
    "description": "Classic pizza with tomato, mozzarella, and basil.",
    "price": 12.99,
    "image": "https://example.com/images/pizza.jpg"
}

###

### Verify the added food
GET http://localhost:5000/api/v1/admin/foods
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

###

### Update a food
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/v1/admin/foods/{{FOOD_ID}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

{
    "name": "Updated Pizza Margherita",
    "cuisine": "Italian",
    "description": "Updated description for the pizza.",
    "price": 14.99,
    "image": "https://example.com/images/updated-pizza.jpg"
}

###

### Delete a food
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/v1/admin/foods/{{FOOD_ID}}
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

###

### Get all reviews
GET http://localhost:5000/api/v1/admin/reviews
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

###

### Delete a review
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/v1/admin/reviews/{{REVIEW_ID}}
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

